data.description:
Up for lease is a spacious home with 4 bedrooms, 3.5 bathrooms available for move-in now. What's better is that this home has 2 master bedrooms, one on each floor. We are looking for responsible and long term tenants with good credit history and stable employment. Home is located in a very nice area with high rating schools from K-12. Additionally, all the amenities that one can ask for are in close proximity such as Publix, Walmart, Lowes, popular restaurants... and easy to hop on & off to all the major freeways. Send us a message to schedule a viewing this weekend. We look forward to having you!!

Preferably long term. Non-smoker, and no pet. For your own protection, please obtain renter insurance before move-in. Tenants are responsible for all utilities.
